  "excerpt": "<p>Experience Working With Armstrong Capital At Armstrong Capital, we thrive in the ever-evolving world of finance, offering services that range from financial planning and mutual fund advisory to comprehensive wealth management. By joining Armstrong Capital, you will gain a holistic work experience that spans across business, finance, economics, and client communications.   Our team is [&hellip;]</p>\n",
  "content": "\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"7480\" class=\"elementor elementor-7480\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-65760cf elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"65760cf\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5da0278\" data-id=\"5da0278\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-43e6def elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"43e6def\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-282adcc\" data-id=\"282adcc\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c3c1fc3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_hero_title\" data-id=\"c3c1fc3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_hero_title.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n    <div class=\"te-box-title sec-title \">        \n        \t\t<h2 class=\"te_title counsolve-size-default\">Experience Working With Armstrong Capital</h2>        \n                <div class=\"normal__text text-box\">\n            <p><p>At Armstrong Capital, we thrive in the ever-evolving world of finance, offering services that range from financial planning and mutual fund advisory to comprehensive wealth management. By joining Armstrong Capital, you will gain a holistic work experience that spans across business, finance, economics, and client communications.</p><p> </p><p>Our team is built on a foundation of a ‘<em><strong>growth mindset</strong></em>,’ where we help you identify and improve your strengths and weaknesses. We’re continuously on the lookout for individuals who can be valuable assets to our team. At Armstrong Capital, you’ll work in a dynamic environment that presents unique challenges every day, fostering innovation and creative problem-solving. Our vibrant team is committed to helping employees grow intellectually, technically, and interpersonally.</p><p> </p><p>We understand the importance of <em><strong>\"work-life balance\"</strong> </em>and believe that an ideal workplace should be engaging, challenging, and rewarding. Whether you’re just starting your career or are an experienced professional, Armstrong Capital provides the right environment to help you achieve your full potential.</p></p>\n        </div>\n                \n    </div>     \n    \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83034f6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_button\" data-id=\"83034f6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;btn_margin&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;top&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;right&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;left&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;isLinked&quot;:true},&quot;btn_margin_tablet&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;top&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;right&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;left&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;isLinked&quot;:true},&quot;btn_margin_mobile&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;top&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;right&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;left&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;isLinked&quot;:true},&quot;btn_padding&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;top&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;right&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;left&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;isLinked&quot;:true},&quot;btn_padding_tablet&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;top&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;right&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;left&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;isLinked&quot;:true},&quot;btn_padding_mobile&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;top&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;right&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;left&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;isLinked&quot;:true},&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \t        \n        <div class=\"btn-box te-btn\">\n            <a href=\"https://armstrong-cap.com/career-send-resume/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"theme-btn btn-two te-thm-btn\">Send Resume</a>\n        </div>               \n    \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7d07224 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7d07224\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3e2fd07 elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_hero_title\" data-id=\"3e2fd07\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_hero_title.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n    <div class=\"te-box-title sec-title \">        \n        \t\t<h2 class=\"te_title counsolve-size-default\">We are in continuous search for individuals who could be the assets in our balance sheet!</h2>        \n                \n    </div>     \n    \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3a6006d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"3a6006d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-680628e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"680628e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-51dce01 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"51dce01\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1350\" src=\"https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-1-min-scaled.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-8217\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-1-min-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-1-min-300x158.jpg 300w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-1-min-1024x540.jpg 1024w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-1-min-768x405.jpg 768w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-1-min-1536x810.jpg 1536w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-1-min-2048x1080.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cbf8d5b e-con-full career-page-box e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"cbf8d5b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d402031 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d402031\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Long-Term Internship </h2>\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0a289fc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0a289fc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Are you a recent graduate looking to gain hands-on experience in the finance industry? Armstrong Capital’s long-term internship program is designed to help you bridge the gap between academic learning and real-world application. Over a period of 6–8 months, you will:</p><p> </p><ul><li><strong>Master the Financial Landscape:</strong> Develop a deep understanding of the financial landscape.</li><li><strong>Build Client Engagement Skills:</strong> Engage with our diverse clientele and learn the art of effective communication.</li><li><strong>Turn Knowledge into Action</strong>: Apply your theoretical knowledge to practical scenarios.</li></ul><p> </p><p>This internship will provide you with invaluable insights and skills that textbooks can’t teach, preparing you for a successful career in finance.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-095876b e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"095876b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a3d25f9 e-con-full career-page-box e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a3d25f9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-87db9a6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"87db9a6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Placement Internship</h2>\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e553213 career-page-box elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e553213\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>If you’re seeking placement opportunities, Armstrong Capital provides an enriching internship experience designed to equip you for the corporate world. As a placement intern, you will:</p><p> </p><ul><li><strong>Client Communication &amp; Marketing: </strong>Initiate client communications and actively participate in social media marketing strategies.</li><li><strong>Financial Planning &amp; Analysis</strong>: Assist in financial planning, fund research, and data analysis to gain practical insights.</li><li><strong>Guidance from Experts:</strong> Work under the guidance of industry experts, following directives to understand professional workflows.</li></ul><p> </p><p>This program is ideal for individuals eager to explore the <strong>finance industry’s dynamics</strong> and evaluate how it aligns with their long-term career goals</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f5ada1a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f5ada1a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ec6f4cc elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ec6f4cc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1709\" src=\"https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career2-min-scaled.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-8218\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career2-min-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career2-min-300x200.jpg 300w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career2-min-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career2-min-370x246.jpg 370w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career2-min-768x513.jpg 768w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career2-min-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career2-min-2048x1367.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-adfb183 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"adfb183\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c3200dc e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c3200dc\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3c7542a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3c7542a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-3.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-8224\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-3.jpg 2560w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-3-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-3-370x246.jpg 370w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-3-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://armstrong-cap.com/wp-content/uploads/Career-3-2048x1366.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1d3907c e-con-full career-page-box e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1d3907c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2633920 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2633920\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Experienced Professionals</h2>\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-850ddb7 career-page-box elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"850ddb7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>At Armstrong Capital, we welcome seasoned professionals eager to bring their expertise to a dynamic, fast-paced environment. Here, you’ll:</p><p> </p><ul><li><strong>Collaborate with Forward-Thinking Professionals</strong>: Join a team of forward-thinking professionals to tackle complex financial challenges and drive meaningful solutions.</li><li><strong>Excel in Core Finance Areas</strong>: Enhance your expertise in wealth management, financial planning, and client advisory services.</li><li><strong>Grow in a Supportive Culture</strong>: Thrive in an environment that values innovation, personal growth, and professional excellence.</li></ul><p> </p><p>Armstrong Capital is the ideal platform for experienced professionals to thrive, embrace fresh challenges, and shape the future of finance.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-1ed78ecf elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"1ed78ecf\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-52eb6acf\" data-id=\"52eb6acf\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-1c15b954 elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"1c15b954\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-d4883aa\" data-id=\"d4883aa\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-911040a elementor-widget elementor-widget-counsolve_hero_title\" data-id=\"911040a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"counsolve_hero_title.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t    \n    <div class=\"te-box-title sec-title \">        \n        \t\t<h2 class=\"te_title counsolve-size-default\">Why Choose Us</h2>        \n                \n    </div>     \n    \n    \t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-1a42b393 elementor-section-full_width elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"1a42b393\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type